{"tid":1365351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[呼籲]727元朗既店舖請你地如常開門做生意","createTime":"2019-07-25T15:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T16:54:09.000Z","uid":195084,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"60a25f6bc81ab330c1bc199de2f53991a0b72d00","tid":1365351,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:19:07.000Z","msg":"經過元朗恐襲之後<br />\n好多舖頭都閂門落閘唔敢再做生意<br />\n而我眼見有唔少香討uwants既香港市民都想身體力行咁反對警黑勾結、無差別恐襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n決定哂727會親身入元朗消費 向紅色恐怖說不 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我希望各位店主會係當日繼續開門口做生意！！ 接待一大班愛國愛港的和理非市民！！！<br />\n我相信到時咁多人入去 個生意額可以補償返早幾日既損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而入去消費既香討uwants友 飲飽食醉之後記得拎返張單呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係會畀d畜牲抹黑你非法集結架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936b0250131288f91270dff128836da5f27b4d3c","tid":1365351,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"無人睇都自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef3b0062ab613b0a8e8076531668ae9a13c1ca7","tid":1365351,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6aa7a304e83400708daafa00653ad575c82b754","tid":1365351,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0c8fbafac6fe1aeadc16d8b7d6f8a42e8c9bd2b6","tid":1365351,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:54:09.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}